title: The Onslaught in Israel Explained
description:
The onslaught continues in Israel as forces from Hamas are persistent in annihilating hundreds of innocent Israeli civilians. There must be justice for Israel, and that justice must arrive soon.

From contributing supplies to Israeli troops to assisting Israel’s medical response teams, here are 5 ways you can play a part in helping Israel through this tragic time:

Friends of the Israel Defense Forces (FIDF): https://www.fidf.org/  

Israel Rescue: http://IsraelRescue.org

American Friends of Magen David Adom: http://Afmda.org

International Fellowship of Christians & Jews: http://IFCJ.org

The Ari Fuld Project: http://AriFuld.org

Watch the full episode here: Ep.1827 - https://youtu.be/KDzTHp-jMRk
